  "synopsis": "The pinnacle of magic was the 9th Circle, a realm said to be that of a demigod. The final key to reaching it was the heart of the Crimson Dragon, Valdrova.\n\n*“I never imagined my own fiancé would come to kill me.”*\n\nYet for some reason, Valdrova offered up her heart without putting up any resistance.\n\n*“…What is this feeling? Why does this leave such a bitter taste?”*\n\nThen I faced it—a despair far older and deeper than the hatred I had carried.\n\n(Source: Naver, translated)",
